			<h2>Anthony, <strong>#CodeMonkey</strong></h2>
			<p>Anthony is an <strong>übergeek</strong> when it comes to handling bits. His favorite dabblings are in <strong>high performance computing with C++</strong> and <strong>front end web development with Ruby (on Rails)</strong> while his knowledge reaches well beyond that. Anthony's preferred domains are <strong>knowledge management</strong> and the automated <strong>mining of intelligence</strong>, but is also proud of his many experiments with <strong>web design</strong>.</p>
			<p>Of course, <strong>Anthony brings more</strong> to the table than just his coding skills. He can help you think <strong>creatively</strong>, <strong>entrepreneurially</strong> and <strong>scientifically</strong> about our approach to your problem.</p>
